cats.description: Meet Morty my new kitten.He is the best! A little bit needy but playful. He  brightens up my day. I love him.

This is Boss. He really thinks he is some millionaire Ceo... Every time I work next to my computer he needs to have a keyboard too... Also, he is always looking at me and judging...He definitely would give me a bad work review... And I am pretty sure he thinks I am his secretary. ;) Love him to death though.
Yep, everytime I need to work. :D Can I use this as an excuse to my boss why I did not finish my project on time?
